'''蜂蘭'''（學名：'''''Ophrys apifera'''''）是[[蜂蘭屬|蜂蘭屬]]下的一種植物，廣泛分佈于[[歐洲|歐洲]]、北非和西亞，且是英國[[貝德福德郡|貝德福德郡]]的郡花。<ref>Plantlife website [http://www.plantlife.org.uk/wild_plants/county_flowers/ ''County Flowers page''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.plantlife.org.uk/wild_plants/county_flowers/ |date=20150430170312 }}</ref> 此外也見於北美洲和東亞。

其種加詞的意思是“有蜂的”，用以指代其蜂狀的花瓣。<ref name="Latindict">[http://www.archives.nd.edu/cgi-bin/wordz.pl?keyword=fer WORDS Latin-to-English Dictionary by William Whittaker, AbleMedia Classics Technology Center] {{Wayback|url=http://www.archives.nd.edu/cgi-bin/wordz.pl?keyword=fer |date=20150923222000 }}, accessed 2014-11-13</ref> 而這種花也會分泌[[利己素|利己素]]模仿雌蜂的氣味，以吸引''[[Tetralonia_cressa|Tetralonia cressa]]''和''[[Eucera_pulveraceae|Eucera pulveraceae]]''這兩種蜂的雄蜂。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Fenster |first1=Charles B. |last2=Marten-Rodrıguez |first2=Silvana |year=2207 |title=Reproductive Assurance and the Evolution of Pollination Specialization |journal=International Journal of Plant Sciences |volume=168 |issue=2 |pages=215–228 |publisher=The University of Chicago |doi=10.1086/509647 |url=http://english.xtbg.cas.cn/rh/rp/200905/P020090810528272663000.pdf |accessdate=2 September 2013 |archive-date=2020-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200519165653/http://english.xtbg.cas.cn/rh/rp/200905/P020090810528272663000.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref> 蜂蘭上最像蜂的花也最有可能吸引到這些蜂，因此就會得到更高的授粉機率。<ref>Dawkins, R. (1986) ''The Blind Watchmaker''</ref>

